  "description": "A simple plugin to prevent excessive Caps in chat!",
  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d913f67056243b606f98a\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640091f01e9e2e54bfd9d454\" /> <a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/anticaps.58129/updates\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d914767056243b606f990\" />  </a> <a href=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/AntiCaps/\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d914767056243b606f98e\" />  </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d914767056243b606f98c\" />  </a>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640092931e9e2e54bfd9d45e\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a420d44776b941b5a1f5f7\" />\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/638a91e9aa2989386ab8ef79\" />  </a>\n\n</center>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Full Transcript</summary>\nAnti Caps\nA mindless solution to prevent caps!\n\nBACKGROUND EFFICIENCY\nThe plugin comes with a fully functional out of the box experience!\n\nNever stops a message from going through with the default configuration. Easy and customizable in simple steps. \n\nCUSTOMIZABLE\nEvery aspect is configurable, without being overloaded!\n\nThis plugin integrates the fully customizable messages protocol. Send clickable components, make chat menus, send URL's and more!\n\n</details>\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/Eh4dDiwVOQA_ExMhPBQbDgEAIVMHCh8APAkEAgEA\" />",
